snippet.title: OvO 1.4.4 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's the 1.4.4 update, with a brand new soundtrack!

Play it on Cool Math Games: https://www.coolmathgames.com/0-ovo

OvO is a fast paced, demanding platformer with more than 50 levels. Join the fun and try to get the best time on all of them !
The game has already been played by hundreds of thousands of players worldwide !

Also, don't hesitate to join the OvO Discord Community to play with other players: https://dedragames.com/ovoDiscord.html
